{
	"info": {
		"_postman_id": "a1b2c3d4-e5f6-7890-abcd-ef1234567890",
		"name": "Auth Laravel Backend API",
		"description": "Postman collection for the Laravel Sanctum auth & e-commerce API.\n\n## Setup\n1. Start the server: `php artisan serve`\n2. Run **Auth → Login** or **Auth → Register** — the token is saved automatically to the `token` collection variable.\n3. Protected routes use Bearer auth via `{{token}}`.\n\n## Variables\n- `base_url` — default `http://localhost:8000/api`\n- `token` — set automatically after login/register\n- `product_id`, `cart_id`, `review_id`, `wishlist_id`, `order_id` — update after creating resources",
		"schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json"
	},
